00e5 trivsel samt god undervisning, men kanskje det aller viktigste ... hver enkelt elev blir sett!"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "0bc81c22eeda178b3760c15fc493e9b2ad147e9ce851e8fae1b6d6fd1614e8b9"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T08:14:05.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "P\u00e5 Nidaros blir elevene sett, noe vi vet er veldig frav\u00e6rende p\u00e5 andre skoler grunnet mange elever og marginal l\u00e6rertetthet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article11877537.ece/pas871/ALTERNATES/w980-default/MDNidarosIdrettsungdomsskole01%20(3).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5c937aa88a905eacc3609c38e88b9543bad47367.jpg?5996e64b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Takk til Nidaros Idrettsungdomsskole! -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "5c937aa88a905eacc3609c38e88b9543bad47367"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["marginal l\u00e6rertetthet", "skoler grunnet", "elev"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "nidaros idrettsungdomsskole"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article11877537.ece/pas871/ALTERNATES/w980-default/MDNidarosIdrettsungdomsskole01%20(3).jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Takk til Nidaros Idrettsungdomsskole!"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no